00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,760
resonate with(共鳴する、心に響く)。

227
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,560
resonate with。

228
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,560
resonate with。

229
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,560
resonate with。

230
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:17,120
